import React from "react"; import styles from "./BudgetPlan.module.css"; const budgetPlans = [ { name: "Vacation", total: 3000, spent: 1200, items: 5, icon: "🏖️" }, { name: "Wedding", total: 10000, spent: 4500, items: 10, icon: "💍" }, { name: "Education", total: 5000, spent: 1000, items: 3, icon: "🎓" }, { name: "Renovation", total: 8000, spent: 2000, items: 4, icon: "🔨" }, { name: "Health", total: 2000, spent: 500, items: 2, icon: "💊" }, ]; const BudgetPlan = () => { return (

MyPlan

Profile

My Budget Plans

+ Create New Plan
{budgetPlans.map((plan, index) => (
{plan.icon} {plan.name} ${plan.total}

{plan.items} Item(s)

${plan.spent} Spent | ${plan.total - plan.spent} Remaining

))}
); }; export default BudgetPlan;
